Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}be they criminals or actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The weird code that Doc came up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:11.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's tougher than the Detective Boys expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who will solve it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.51,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One hot summer day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:46.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we were out to collect bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Doc gave us a code quiz,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:52.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"marumushi ni tento", which would lead us to where a treasure was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I couldn't solve the code either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:59.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Meanwhile, Ran and Sonoko called me from the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}saying there was a murder at the hotel where they were staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko remembered seeing some strange writing{14:05}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the window of the room where the murder took place...{14:09}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange writing?{14:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like some kind of code...{14:18}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who found the body?{17:14}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three of Miyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friends!{17:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were going out to dinner together.{17:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Miyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't show up on time, they went to his room and found the door unlocked.{17:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They went inside and found Miyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lying on the ground under a broken window.{17:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what they told the police.{17:47}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After that, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe the "tento" part of the code refers to the Tentō Festival!{21:43}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's the case, I don't understand the "marumushi" in front of it.{21:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:03:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's in the direction of the Marumushi Hot Spring!{22:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Marumushi ni tentō" - "Light up the Marumushi"...{22:16}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?{arere}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's some mysterious gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get real. Take a closer look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're carrying washbowls, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The village probably bought this run-down inn on the cheap and turned it into a public bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bath... sentō...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe tento is really sentō! You know, a public bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now see, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, that "te" doesn't look like a "se".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's not tentō, as in "light", either. It's clearly spelled tento.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Genta. You can't just collapse and give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember what Doc said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said we might be able to solve the code if we lay down and thought about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if we're stuck, we should splash water on our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we've got a public bath here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take her advice and wash off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooh, good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trust me, you won't find anything in that inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure... I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if a {\i1}certain someone{\i0} also gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Give up, my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A text...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:10.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, I thought Sonoko had her bag stolen with her cell phone inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"I found this bag abandoned on a street,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but there was nothing to identify the owner by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:22.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I checked the cell phone I found inside the bag
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:26.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and decided to send a message to the most recent person on the list of calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:32.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I would like to send the bag to you, so please give me your name and address."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh, I guess the purse snatcher threw Sonoko's bag away after stealing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why isn't this person asking me for the address of the owner of the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:49.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why text me? Wouldn't it be easier to just call someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You give up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:02.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or they could hand the bag over to the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just received a text from someone who claims to have found Sonoko's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may contact you too. Wait for the call...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:16.94,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My phone's almost dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm at the police station now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'll call you back as soon as we get to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you told them the message might be "tel shite", "please call"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police and Miyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s three friends said that could be a possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't identify the murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we're going back to the hotel for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful. That purse snatcher could still be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to drive me and your wife to the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran told you, didn't she? Miyama's hot college friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are his other two friends there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... It'll be just us and Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police are taking a long time to question Yanuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the late Miyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s been waiting for her to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} walked back to the hotel on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yanuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is crying and the police still have questions for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s going to drive us to the hotel and then come back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:40.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I'd better hang up! My phone's almost dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wish I'd gone to the beach with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the beach, I found a jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't find a jellyfish in the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish when it's upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jellyfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does look like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish when it's upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see... So that's what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lie down and splash water on your face, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}a code like this gave me trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But sometimes, simple codes are the hardest to decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been long enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just tell us the secret code?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does "marumushi ni tento" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Until you all give up, my lips are sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I give up! Whisper it to me! Where's the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No fair, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why did I suddenly think of Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't solved it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be a sore loser, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys give up too easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like even Shin'ichi is stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's think about this carefully from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, the code is written in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can understand "marumushi" and "tento" being written in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the same time, doesn't it seem strange that a word like "ni" would be written that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secondly, if you look closely, each character is strangely crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doc's just got bad handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thirdly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we've got the clues Doc and Haibara gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did they ever give us clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Lie down and think about it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and "if you don't get it, splash some water on your face."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those aren't things they normally say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they want us to lie down and look at the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lie down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything different...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, for a sec I thought I had it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you or didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I was sure the message would say something sideways!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the smirk on his smug little face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's solved it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even sideways, it doesn't look like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's think about the other clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing about washing your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to wash up in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still think we're supposed to go to that in the villagers use as a public bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara and the Doc already told us there's nothing at the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then where are we supposed to wash up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she didn't literally mean "wash your face".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's think. What do you do when you wash your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn on the tap...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wash up in the running water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wipe my face with a towel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we're talking about when you wash your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I wash my face, I eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I look in the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You don't see anything in the mirror but yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just gets more baffling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I think you're on to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,see how that hot spring logo looks like a jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when it's upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:13:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But none of these letters look like fish upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't look like words either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you have to do both!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn the message sideways and reflect it in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we turn it sideways, flip it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hold it up to the moonlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,(ムラマツリノトリイ MU RA MA TSU RI NO TO RI I)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"muramatsuri no tori'i" - "the shrine of the village festival"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"muramatsuri no tori'i"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's that shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? Doc? Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go see what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you taught the kids they can figure things out on their own if they put their minds to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. I'm a heck of a guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to go look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to find out what the treasure is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The code points to that brightly-lit tori'i gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you smeared some tree sap onto it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet it's swarming with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rhinoceros beetles and stag beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you came up with this secret code.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A message that can be read from different directions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to use animals for the code first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I taped animal names to the window to get ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I was doing that, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was watching from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't "oxygen" too advanced for the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... "kirin" (キリン) or "giraffe" looked like "sanso" (サンソ) from the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then you thought of the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shining through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what it meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought of Ran a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's in serious danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, we're on the way back to the hotel in Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of the car right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've figured out the real meaning of "teiu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a small splotch in front of the "t"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The message was written sideways,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but stand it up and flip it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it spells the murderer's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The battery's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it? What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about standing up and flipping over the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like your husband's jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Ran and Sonoko are involved in a murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko happened to see the letters of a message written by a man who was bludgeoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was written horizontally in lowercase letters that spelled "teiu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More precisely, there was a little mark in front of the "t",
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the "i" was an "l" and the "u" looked like a hiragana "shi" (し).
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's exactly like "muramatsuri no tori'i".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The message is written sideways and backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"marumushi ni tento"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you turn "sanso" on its side and read it backwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kirin".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what's "teiu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,かのう - the characters for "Kano".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did the victim leave such a difficult code as a dying message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no code!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collapsed on the floor and wrote the name on the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Sonoko saw it from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to tell Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, but Ran's phone went dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to top it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran and Sonoko are in Kano's car right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't the road to the hotel, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Where's the hotel they're staying at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I knew that, I would've called the cops already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All Ran told me was that she was going to the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! I should've realized it sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I got that weird text message from Sonoko's stolen phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to delete the picture with the dying message from my cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he asked for my name and address...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} guy you were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a teen detective, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's cool! Dating a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! He's not my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're such a cute couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I sent him a photo of Ran in her swimsuit this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pity Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} isn't here with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would've loved to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that sleuth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the murderer is waiting for me to contact him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he must have Sonoko's phone on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Listen to that ringtone, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ringtone's the same as your phone, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, rather, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is{\i0} my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed it off you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to get rid of the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we get deeper into the woods, I've got some questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,about the whereabouts of that Shin'ichi brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They still haven't picked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone's picked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't "hello" me! Where the hell were you when Ran needed you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:33.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey! Are you listening to me?!{possibly missing the end of the line}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could've been hurt when the car crashed into that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was, we had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's side kick went straight into the driver's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:59.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After that, Sonoko called the police, and the murderer was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:02.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The victim had been blackmailing Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:06.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}threatening to reveal the fact that he'd cheated his way into college.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:13.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was the same old story of one crime snowballing into another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:16.58,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:17.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:20.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought I saved it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we deleted that swimsuit photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Kids can't look at that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} erase it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:42.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}DAMN!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Magure's such a great show, isn't it?{DCTP 2:26}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really outdid yourselves with the trick that time.{DCTP 3:07}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is one of the drama's three scriptwriters, isn't he?{DCTP 4:20}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:02.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Such an aggressive look in his eyes...{DCTP 13:21}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's definitely the culprit.{DCTP 13:24}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:09.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yet he has so much confidence in his trick.{DCTP 13:28}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:16.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.11,0:24:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Two cups
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode's title...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:25.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If it's half-finished, then maybe it's a boxed eel lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.30,0:24:26.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Eh?
